name: InfStones
description: InfStones is an advanced, enterprise-grade Platform as a Service (PaaS) blockchain infrastructure provider trusted by the top blockchain companies in the world. InfStones' infrastructure provides support on over 80 blockchains. InfStones is trusted by Binance, Lido, Swell, OKX, Chainlink, Harmony, KuCoin, and many more.
